HEADWORD: Postscutellum
<hw>Post`scu*tel"lum</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL. See
<er>Post-</er>, and <er>Scutellum</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>The hindermost dorsal piece of a thoracic somite of an insect; the
plate behind the scutellum.</def>⟦br⟧
